  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of BGG492 as Adjunctive Treatment in Patients With Partial Onset Seizures</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 12-week, Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Efficacy and Safety Study Examining Seizure Frequency of BGG492 Capsules as Adjunctive Treatment in Patients With Partial Onset Seizures</official_title>
